{"tid":615311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2男錢銀糾紛互毆 3樓打到落街","createTime":"2018-04-03T09:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T09:20:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"782c586ead053170d5a115a0f1c566faa481015c","tid":615311,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:14:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180403/20351072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F20351072&d=HAiivWGNPlOEYzJ8e6jWn8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a4970098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180403%2F20351072&h=aa9dca5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180403/20351072</a><br />\n<br />\n2男錢銀糾紛互毆<br />\n3樓打到落街<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】尖沙嘴彌敦道62號美麗都大廈，昨晨1時許，兩名同樣39歲、持行街紙外籍男子，疑因金錢糾紛爭執，在大廈3樓走廊互毆，並沿樓梯追逐至地下。警員接報趕至現場，持盾牌制止及展開調查，兩人均告受傷，事後一併被捕送院治理。"},{"pid":"6899c81e8d5c523755577d4c32fdde855ad7c812","tid":615311,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"葉問？"},{"pid":"ab6473f1b3a44fdb822dbb48465b2d426da32971","tid":615311,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"我識得既南亞人好nice.mp3"},{"pid":"49328231ce8f2f475164e63555c94edba6cc2af5","tid":615311,"uid":33972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"行街紙外籍男子...<br />\n即係咩籍先?"},{"pid":"8e39340fac463b9d44612a45ead3bf4c35219e90","tid":615311,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8206a03e95f492b3c2163305d60db0df90935a8","tid":615311,"uid":171901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-0